# Router-on-a-Stick (Inter-VLAN Routing) â€“ Packet Tracer

This project shows how to let devices in different VLANs communicate by using **Router-on-a-Stick**.  
A single router interface is divided into sub-interfaces, each assigned to a VLAN.

